{"tid":658158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平想趕川普前見金正恩　北韓拒絕：川金會比較重要","createTime":"2018-05-08T17:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T06:55:31.000Z","uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ceabcbbad41fc6f09f7f86521b2106dd1287088","tid":658158,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"北韓領導人金正恩密訪北京時，習近平曾允諾將回訪北韓。日本朝日新聞報導，中方近日向北韓提議於川金會前訪朝，卻遭到拒絕。金正恩認為，現階段應以「川金會為首要優先處理事項」。據傳，北韓近期與美韓對話時，皆未提到中朝兩國一直以來堅守的「美軍撤離朝鮮半島」要求，而中國也對此頗有微詞。<br />\n<br />\n根據《朝日新聞》報導，北韓消息人士透露，金正恩3月出訪北京會晤中國國家主席習近平時，曾邀請對方回訪北韓。中國對外連絡部長宋濤日前前往北韓與會時，也曾與北韓協商習近平出訪相關事宜，其中，中方曾向北韓要求在川金會前舉行第二次的「習金會」，但遭到朝方以「必須以美朝高峰會為優先」為由拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，北韓將不會在川金會時，要求美方撤除駐韓美軍，此舉引起中國強烈不滿。中國認為，隨著1953年所簽定的停戰協定轉變為和平協定，由美軍主導的聯合國軍隊扮演的角色消失，屆時，駐韓美軍存在的意義也相對薄弱。事實上，日前金正恩會晤美國中情局局長蓬佩奧時，並未要求美方撤除駐韓美軍，因此也引發國際社會討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，據傳金正恩3月訪中時，曾向中國國家主席習近平表示，如果川金會破局，為了對抗美國的對朝軍事力，必要時將請求中方的全力支援。這卻與金正恩遲遲未向美方提出美軍撤離朝鮮半島的要求有所違背。對此，北韓不願具名的相關人士透露，金正恩此舉是意圖分化中美兩國，藉此對北韓製造有利的國際局勢。<br />\n<br />\n根據《日本經濟》報導，川金會結束後，習近平將出訪平壤，至於出訪日期則有可能會訂在北韓成立正確70周年的9月9日前後。"},{"pid":"530707d2388c6ea914cbd9b1e2176c4734b67c7d","tid":658158,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最</span></span>"},{"pid":"1de34706de8fc62386711a31e1dcd591f4704431","tid":658158,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又畀侵侵撚到一棟都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b268fc10eb166cfd0593e24d622cfe3316a8efa3","tid":658158,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"金正恩此舉是意圖分化中美兩國，藉此對北韓製造有利的國際局勢<br />\n<br />\n北韓依啲窮國都尚且識得係大國間攞利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380b84d027b406adf4968b16e0d877bce4ad4a92","tid":658158,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T18:38:28.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141ba825c1bff276f2e0533be628182addb52e8a","tid":658158,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"國際毒撚小支支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318ee301caf275d8a33db71ec4916c6b4091e53c","tid":658158,"uid":164383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20180508/kim-jong-un-xi-jinping-china-north-korea/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fasia-pacific%2F20180508%2Fkim-jong-un-xi-jinping-china-north-korea%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=YutFC7m1wFMtogwEPGPStzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=edbec17a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20180508/kim-jong-un-xi-jinping-china-north-korea/zh-hant/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>金正恩與習近平在大連會面</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa8883657d0f4e8b9a6f3235e665508d7e00747","tid":658158,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"318ee301caf275d8a33db71ec4916c6b4091e53c","tid":658158,"uid":164383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:16:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20180508/kim-jong-un-xi-jinping-china-north-korea/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fasia-pacific%2F20180508%2Fkim-jong-un-xi-jinping-china-north-korea%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=YutFC7m1wFMtogwEPGPSt